            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white group-hover:text-primary transition-colors duration-300 mb-2">Sophie Earley</h3>
            <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Won two Bronze medals at the Junior European Championships and played professional in France.</p>
          </div>
